<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>O GOD, OUR HELP IN AGES PAST</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien hun lui a ei panpih,
 Hun thaka kinepna;
 Huih lauhum a ka kiselnau,
 Leh ka kumsawt In uh.

[V2]
 2. Na Lalchutphah lim nuoi achun,
 Na mithiengte a cheng;
 Na ban tun mai le kei u di'n,
 Ka hinnau khawp ahi.

[V3]
 3. Tanghaw ana dindawk mau leh,
 Lei akisiem ma'n le;
 Kumsawt in nang Pathien na hi,
 Lamdang ngeilo kumkhuo'n.

[V4]
 4. Nang ngaih in kum sang tampi le,
 Nitak khat bang ahi;
 Ni suoh kit kal a zan beihna,
 Zanven bangin a chawm.

[V5]
 5. Hun in tuilien luong zing bang in,
 Mihingte a tawk mang;
 Zingkal a mang a man bangin,
 Hetloh in hun a bei.

[V6]
 6. Pathien hun lui a ei panpih,
 Hun thak-a kinepna;
 Nang chu damsung a ei vengpa,
 Leh ka kumsawt In hi'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>14</hymn_number>
<author>Croft, William (1678-1727), Watts, Isaac (1674-1748)</author>
</song>